---
layout: base.njk
pageKey: grow
title: "Industries — what we build, by business type"
permalink: grow.html
description: Web design, AI assistants, and booking systems built for your industry — dentists, restaurants, law firms, real estate, fitness studios, and nonprofits across the Bay Area. Start with a free scan.
---

{# ===== Hero =========================================================== #}
<section class="section section--tight has-aurora">
  <div class="aurora" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="container container--narrow center">
    <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">Industries</span>
    <h1 class="section__title">What we build, by business type</h1>
    <p class="section__lead">
      The work looks different for a dental practice than a restaurant. Pick your service and
      your industry — we’ll show you exactly what we’d build, and what it changes. Or skip
      ahead and get a free scan of your current site.
    </p>
    <div class="btn-row btn-row--center mt-6">
      <a class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" href="{{ site.cta.url }}">Get my free scan</a>
      <a class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg" href="buy.html">See packages</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== Service hubs =================================================== #}
<section class="section section--tight">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__head section__head--center" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">By service</span>
      <h2 class="section__title">Start with what you need</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid--3">
      {% for svc in growServices %}
        <a class="card card__link" href="grow-{{ svc.key }}.html" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="{{ loop.index0 }}">
          <span class="card__title">{{ svc.label }}</span>
          <span class="card__text">See {{ svc.label | lower }} built for each industry we serve.</span>
        </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== Full index by service ========================================= #}
{% for svc in growServices %}
  <section class="section section--tight">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__head section__head--center" data-reveal>
        <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">{{ svc.label }}</span>
        <h2 class="section__title">{{ svc.label }} by industry</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid--auto">
        {% for lp in landingPages %}
          {% if lp.serviceKey == svc.key and lp.tier == "A" %}
            <a class="card card__link" href="{{ lp.permalink }}" data-reveal>
              <span class="card__title">{{ lp.nicheLabel }}</span>
            </a>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
{% endfor %}

{# ===== Closing CTA =================================================== #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-band" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="cta-band__title">Not sure where to start?</h2>
      <p class="cta-band__text">
        Send us your link. We’ll scan it free and point you to the smallest thing that moves the
        needle for your business.
      </p>
      <div class="btn-row btn-row--center">
        <a class="btn btn--light btn--lg" href="{{ site.cta.url }}">Get my free scan</a>
        <a class="btn btn--secondary btn--lg" href="services.html">See all services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
